,{"pid":"c3cb5dca2e623170e93ab610501c89468a3c56f0","tid":827915,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"好賺穩賺交返比政府<br />\n硬骨頭蝕錢先比私人市場？<br />\n<br />\n真係on9無極限"},{"pid":"cd89dc9f30f160006576389bbf93644aff19a4be","tid":827915,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正宗過河拆橋</blockquote><br />\n咁多年都睇唔清中共咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7e/Usedcondom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F7%2F7e%2FUsedcondom.jpg&h=72d6284d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}